  "title": "URGENT HIRE: Junior Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Stationed at the site office and work on alternate Saturdays as required.</li><li>Source and procure sub-contractors and suppliers, collating prices for comparison.</li><li>Review and understand all specifications and construction drawings to ensure accuracy in project costing.</li><li>Prepare cost-loading documentation to facilitate effective project management.</li><li>Collaborate with project teams to monitor costs and budgets throughout the construction process.</li><li>Provide timely cost estimates and support for variations and claims as necessary.</li><li>Maintain clear communication with clients, contractors, and stakeholders regarding project costs and status.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Building Construction, Quantity Surveying, or equivalent.</li><li>Relevant experience in quantity surveying for construction projects.</li><li>Strong analytical and numerical skills.</li><li>Excellent communication and negotiation abilities.</li><li>Proficiency in cost estimating software and Microsoft Excel.</li><li>Attention to detail and a comprehensive understanding of construction methods and materials.</li></ul><p>If interested, please submit your application to cvs@jdawms.com with your expected salary and resume.</p><p>We regret that only short-listed candidates will be contacted shortly. By submitting your application or resume, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and sharing of your personal information with potential employers for their assessment.</p><p>JDA WMS Pte Ltd | EA Personnel: Pham Thi Tuyet Mai </p><p>EA License No: 23S1595 | EA Registration No: R25127838</p>",
